    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir海外ツアー　追加公演ファイナル",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1966.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、入っていいか？　応援に来たぞ\n葵の好きな店のスイーツも差し入れに持って来たんだ",
      "startTime": 7.3666667461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}君か\nいいけど、本当にわざわざ日本から来たんだね",
      "startTime": 13.2270974238,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6087.2564316,
          "startTime": 16.9476873439
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、せっかくの海外追加公演だし\nせめてファイナルくらいはこの目で見たいと思ってな",
      "startTime": 20.7666657924,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 547.6882182000011,
          "startTime": 18.0081181768
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、てっきり今回はさとみに\n任せっきりだと思ってたから驚いたよ",
      "startTime": 26.8333323796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "最近、やけにリズノワには冷たいからさ\nBIG4になったら、もう僕らなんて興味ないの？",
      "startTime": 33.4898401339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君があまりに冷たいから\n僕は毎晩、枕を涙で濡らしてるんだよ？",
      "startTime": 39.8565068006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは嘘だろ。でも少しでもそう思わせていたらすまん\nLizNoirに興味がなくなる、なんてありえない",
      "startTime": 49.5333324591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ、冗談だよ。でも君からそんな\nラブコールを聞けるなんてね。冗談の甲斐があったよ",
      "startTime": 58.5812009255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、わざわざアメリカまで来たんだから\n僕らのステージを楽しんでいってよ",
      "startTime": 65.5478675921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "今回の舞台演出は、僕もアイデアを出したんだ\n君は前回のツアーのこと、覚えてる？",
      "startTime": 72.0478675921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にオフを過ごしたことがあったでしょ\nあの日の出来事が、今回の舞台演出のきっかけだよ",
      "startTime": 78.1478675921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "前回っていうと、リズノワの初めての海外ツアーか\n確か、BIG4になってすぐのことだったよな……",
      "startTime": 87.3666657924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカに行ったのは、あれが二回目だけどね\nまぁ、一回目は望んで行った訳じゃなかったけど",
      "startTime": 94.7502034584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "当時は島流しにされたと思ってたよ\nLizNoirはここで朽ち果てるんだってね",
      "startTime": 101.8333324591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカ行きは、朝倉さんの指示だったよな\n朝倉さんは、意味なくそんなことをする人じゃないよ",
      "startTime": 108.7333324591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "うん。今なら分かるし、朝倉さんは大恩人だよ\n今の僕らは、沢山の恩人に支えられて出来上がったんだ",
      "startTime": 117.7373688141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "そう\n僕が君と一緒に会いに行った、あの人にも――",
      "startTime": 124.3707021474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――前回の海外ライブツアー　オフ日",
      "startTime": 129.1707023025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "オンボロだったと聞いてはいたけど、こんな所に\nアイドルが四人住んでいたのか……信じられないな",
      "startTime": 135.7666657924,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 131.5666657924
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "今考えれば凄いよね。インターフォンすらないんだ\nセキュリティーとか酷くない？",
      "startTime": 145.1617634217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "こんな部屋に住んでいた僕達が、今やこの国で\nライブツアーか……。随分遠くまで来た気がするよ",
      "startTime": 151.2852347399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……今はBIG4になって初の海外ツアー中で\n今日は貴重なオフ日だろ。どうしてここに来たんだ？",
      "startTime": 159.6666657924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "他のメンバーと同じように、オフを楽しめばいいのに\n今からでも、みんなと一緒にショッピングに……",
      "startTime": 167.9999991257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "君こそ、わざわざ日本から来たんだ\n僕より、みんなの方に行けば良かったのに",
      "startTime": 173.6363868474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "葵が海外でも単独行動しようとするのを\n見過ごせなかったんだよ",
      "startTime": 179.700000143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "それ、僕のことが気になるから……じゃなくて\n危なっかしいって言いたいんだね。顔に出てるよ",
      "startTime": 185.700000143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "僕はこう見えて、立派に成長してるんだよ？　君だって\n後輩の面倒を良く見てるって褒めてくれてたじゃないか",
      "startTime": 194.9676799852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "面倒見が良くなったのは認めるけど\n葵は目を離すと何をしでかすか分からないから……",
      "startTime": 202.100000143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカに来てからは、大したことしてないよ\nライブ前の暇な時間に、街中で踊ったくらいじゃない？",
      "startTime": 209.1333272934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "本番を目前に控えたトップアイドルが\n路上でゲリラライブをやるのは、大したことなんだよ",
      "startTime": 215.1666607062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "でもみんな、喜んでくれてたよ。それがきっかけで\n僕らのファンになってくれるかもしれないし",
      "startTime": 223.1333273728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "こころから多少聞いてはいたが、さすがにライブ当日は\n……莉央さんはどんな反応だったんだ？",
      "startTime": 231.5999940395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "どうだったかな……そういえば、本気で怒ってたかな？\n何十分も説教を聞かされたような気がする",
      "startTime": 240.5666607062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "もう絶対、そういうのは勘弁してくれ……\n今や世界の井川葵なんだ。何かあったら大変だろ",
      "startTime": 248.3379684867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、考えておくよ\nそんなことより{user}君、僕はね",
      "startTime": 256.119736425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-noon.webp",
