      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（……葵らしいな。でも、それならいつかまた）\n（ツアーに来た時、ここを借りてもいいかもしれない）",
      "startTime": 271.4333273728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
